{
 "name": "RPlog_Torments_and_Temptations",
 "title": "Torments and Temptations: A Night Out on Calamari",
 "summary": "In the barracks on Mon Calamari, Lando Calrissian hires the archaeologist Paul to track down the Mandalorian Grathix and recover possibly Force-active Jedi artifacts, while Paul warns of a dangerous red-haired smuggler named Vermilion who has menaced both him and Jessalyn. After Lando leaves, an intimate, painful conversation between Paul and Jessalyn about loneliness and her secret past is interrupted by the teenager Shenner, and Paul retreats to a tavern with Shenner and Tacra to drink. Drunk and reckless, Paul dances with a stranger; a jealous Shenner cuts in and kisses him, provoking a heated argument outside in which she confesses she loves him and he, intoxicated, kisses her back before guiltily pushing her away over their age difference. Jessalyn discovers them, and Paul flees into the cold ocean; she follows, and the two wounded friends comfort each other in the surf. Paul resolves to leave the barracks to do his work on Mandalore and clear the air, giving Jessalyn a contact card and a promise to return, while a heartbroken Shenner is sent home.",
